
Initialize the application:
- Load data from localStorage.
- Set up the user interface.


Handle user input and selections:
- Generate ticket based on selected numbers.
- Calculate ticket price.
- Update display with calculated price.


Simulate draw and determine winners:
- Generate winning numbers.
- Compare user tickets with winning numbers.
- Update ticket objects with win/loss status.
- Display results to users.


Update data and display results:
- Save updated data to localStorage.
- Display results and notifications to users.
